#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:110
msgid "Experiment Details"
msgstr "實驗細節"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:112
msgid ""
"**Random seeds.** All experiments were run for 10 random seeds each. "
"Graphs show the average (solid line) and std dev (shaded) of performance "
"over random seed over the course of training."
msgstr ""
"**隨機種子 (Random Seeds)。** 所有實驗均使用 10 個隨機種子分別執行。"
"圖表顯示了訓練過程中各隨機種子的效能平均值（實線）和標準差（陰影區域）。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:114
msgid ""
"**Performance metric.** Performance for the on-policy algorithms is "
"measured as the average trajectory return across the batch collected at "
"each epoch. Performance for the off-policy algorithms is measured once "
"every 10,000 steps by running the deterministic policy (or, in the case "
"of SAC, the mean policy) without action noise for ten trajectories, and "
"reporting the average return over those test trajectories."
msgstr ""
"**效能指標。** 同策略 (On-policy) 演算法的效能以每個訓練週期 (Epoch) 收集的"
"批次中軌跡回報 (Trajectory Return) 的平均值來衡量。離策略 (Off-policy) 演算法"
"的效能每 10,000 步測量一次，方法是在不加動作雜訊的情況下運行確定性策略 "
"(Deterministic Policy)（或者在 SAC 的情況下，運行平均策略）十條軌跡，並報告"
"這些測試軌跡的平均回報。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:116
msgid ""
"**Network architectures.** The on-policy algorithms use networks of size "
"(64, 32) with tanh units for both the policy and the value function. The "
"off-policy algorithms use networks of size (256, 256) with relu units."
msgstr ""
"**網路架構。** 同策略演算法的策略 (Policy) 和價值函數 (Value Function) 均使用"
"大小為 (64, 32) 且帶有 tanh 啟動函數的網路。離策略演算法使用大小為 "
"(256, 256) 且帶有 relu 啟動函數的網路。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:118
msgid ""
"**Batch size.** The on-policy algorithms collected 4000 steps of agent-"
"environment interaction per batch update. The off-policy algorithms used "
"minibatches of size 100 at each gradient descent step."
msgstr ""
"**批次大小 (Batch Size)。** 同策略演算法每次批次更新收集 4000 步的智能體-"
"環境互動資料。離策略演算法在每個梯度下降 (Gradient Descent) 步驟中使用大小為 "
"100 的小批次 (Minibatch)。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:120
msgid ""
"All other hyperparameters are left at default settings for the Spinning "
"Up implementations. See algorithm pages for details."
msgstr ""
"所有其他超參數 (Hyperparameters) 均保留 Spinning Up 實作的預設值。"
"詳情請參閱各演算法頁面。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:122
msgid "Learning curves are smoothed by averaging over a window of 11 epochs."
msgstr "學習曲線透過在 11 個訓練週期的視窗內取平均值進行平滑處理。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:124
msgid "You Should Know"
msgstr "你應該知道"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:126
msgid ""
"By comparison to the literature, the Spinning Up implementations of DDPG,"
" TD3, and SAC are roughly at-parity with the best reported results for "
"these algorithms. As a result, you can use the Spinning Up "
"implementations of these algorithms for research purposes."
msgstr ""
"與文獻相比，Spinning Up 的 DDPG、TD3 和 SAC 實作與這些演算法的最佳報告結果"
"大致持平。因此，你可以將這些演算法的 Spinning Up 實作用於研究目的。"

#: ../../spinningup/bench.rst:128
msgid ""
"The Spinning Up implementations of VPG, TRPO, and PPO are overall a bit "
"weaker than the best reported results for these algorithms. This is due "
"to the absence of some standard tricks (such as observation normalization"
" and normalized value regression targets) from our implementations. For "
"research comparisons, you should use the implementations of TRPO or PPO "
"from `OpenAI Baselines`_."
msgstr ""
"Spinning Up 的 VPG、TRPO 和 PPO 實作整體上比這些演算法的最佳報告結果稍弱。"
"這是因為我們的實作中缺少一些標準技巧（如觀測值正規化和正規化的價值迴歸目標）。"
"如需用於研究比較，你應該使用 `OpenAI Baselines`_ 中的 TRPO 或 PPO 實作。"

